data.text:
Joey Goes Hollywood

Joey is cast in a new "Beach Party" television series with the stars of the original 1960s movies, FRANKIE AVALON and ANNETTE FUNICELLO. The whole family visits Hollywood for the taping of the pilot.

The Seavers vs. the Cleavers

Jason (ALAN THICKE) and Maggie (JOANNA KERNS) are displeased after being labeled unacceptable parents by prim P.T.A. member June Hinckley (ANNETTE FUNICELLO).

The Missing Father

Zorro must protect a young woman (Annette Funicello) who just arrived from Spain.
